wdi-GC.TAX.OTHR.CN.def: Other taxes include employer payroll or labor taxes, taxes on property, and taxes not allocable to other categories, such as penalties for late payment or nonpayment of taxes.
wdi-GC.TAX.OTHR.CN.name: Other taxes
